name: suirex
description: REX is a cute blue dino on the sui blockchain. What makes REX stand out from the rest, in a visual way, is it's a 'reptile' on a water blockchain. Rex has amassed a huge cult following on socials, a strong and active community which is evident by the engagement metrics on social media. Rex aims to be more than a meme with a marketable appearance it can easily be merchandised and expanded merchandise such as toys.
